# workflow-diagnosis

Use this when the cause is unclear.

1. Read the project context files.
2. Gather evidence before editing.
3. Trace from runtime entry points: {{inlineList architecture.runtimeEntryPoints}}.
4. Check whether the issue touches contracts or dangerous modules.
5. Output root-cause hypotheses and recommended next step.

Stop before editing if root cause is uncertain or the task is Tier 3.
